{"tid":1543570,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"HKU醫科生：支持勇武，唔會同前線割席，五大訴求缺一不可！","createTime":"2019-09-05T08:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:05:07.000Z","uid":36592,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed8daf8235e6ef14d5ff84ab576a2854b758573","tid":1543570,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/69285552_2429275117158094_7634075975164100608_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_oc=AQmjutzYkK3AbeXHszDlubrAvYNIy4X9XsKktupnYmxiqH6FtW_PMquoy5tNPkWhSko&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=5bb09ea0ac3de08f3d836b52d03750b4&amp;oe=5E0EDCC4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F69285552_2429275117158094_7634075975164100608_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_oc%3DAQmjutzYkK3AbeXHszDlubrAvYNIy4X9XsKktupnYmxiqH6FtW_PMquoy5tNPkWhSko%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D5bb09ea0ac3de08f3d836b52d03750b4%26oe%3D5E0EDCC4&h=ccfcfc5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本週開學後相繼有學生聲援反修訂《逃犯條例》行動，香港大學醫學院學生今午在沙宣道校園築成人鏈，逾300學生穿黑衫、戴口罩，部分人以紗布遮蓋右眼表態。有身穿白袍出席的醫科生認為，港府只回應一項訴求「絕對不能接受」，又說港人在過去三個月失去太多，認為需要回應五大訴求，改變制度。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">身穿白袍、戴頭盔及「豬嘴」的港大醫科生王同學表示，作為未來的醫生，絕對不是特首早前形容在社會「無位置」（have no stake in the society）的年輕人，希望告知勇武派抗爭者，醫科生亦支持他們的行動，不會與前線「割席」。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，在過去三個月港人失去的太多，包括逾1000人被捕，或面臨被起訴暴動罪，有「手足」接連以死相諫，以及3人眼睛受傷等，形容「卡數還min pay（最低還款額）都不夠」，重申五大訴求缺一不可。他指出，港人不會滿足於此，目前需要制度上的改變，需要民主自由，會繼續與抗爭者站在同一陣線。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n護理系學生鄧同學曾到前線做急救工作，他表示不少醫學院學生曾在為示威者急救時被警方阻撓，加上8．31事件中警方一度阻止消防處救護員進入太子站，又有義務救護員被要求面壁，他認為不可接受。他親眼目睹不少示威者被警棍所傷，「好多受傷都是源於警察發洩，責任都是在警察身上」。對於警方稱衝突現場有「自稱救護員」，未能確認身份，亦有「搶犯」的風險，他指出現場荷槍實彈的防暴警察眾多，反問如何搶犯，「唔通我哋全部畀佢射殺咩？愈高級的（警察）講嘢愈無稽，張開眼講大話」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，國父孫中山是港大醫學院前身、香港華人西醫書院首屆畢業生，港大醫學院蒙民偉樓豎立孫中山的銅像，有學生貼上「五大訴求、缺一不可」的標語，並為銅像穿上反光衣及戴頭盔。另有學生在人鏈中傳遞一個戴著頭盔口罩、染紅紗布遮蓋右眼的鬆弛熊公仔。<br />\n<br />\nSource:明報<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190905/s00001/1567669183726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190905%2Fs00001%2F1567669183726&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=6cb1224c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190905%2Fs00001%2F1567669183726&h=8595b89e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190905/s00001/1567669183726</a>"},{"pid":"a799eb97386c7c894c6547a4627f1f28c45cd9c3","tid":1543570,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:37:24.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"456c0a3c1aa9b1b1b11a38b5f69306ed5e510275","tid":1543570,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:38:47.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01a0d06174cec05083429133837c221d51aa8a","tid":1543570,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass