f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0de61fd13fde1d10de97bdda3b094caa0e30d9","tid":1543570,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:45:40.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f53cfcd208f7c95ecfbc7af43241f6572444799","tid":1543570,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 出咗不反對啦！【9月6 反濫捕 抗威權 遮打集會】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1543083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1543083</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTsuWvi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTsuWvi.jpg&h=59781468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ud9tv0z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUd9tv0z.jpg&h=17d13451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9154e69bf5352eccf090ef8bff7a2c50f1afeeda","tid":1543570,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559603a4fabac93ed0712f04d0d3b2bb3521b31e","tid":1543570,"uid":81008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7225ddf67d4933c5bf671c8b903f44078d1936b","tid":1543570,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n分別在於：<br />\n<br />\n殉港手足：<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\nZhita Wu（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019 <br />\n何小姐（27歲） - 4/9/2019<br />\n9人離世<br />\n<br />\n還有：<br />\n4隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2LPVhj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2LPVhj.jpg&h=35c3dac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4TBAhk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4TBAhk.jpg&h=05bdd3d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8udugLx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8udugLx.jpg&h=bae3ed34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZTBFS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZTBFS9.jpg&h=3e1d2264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=g6cJT0UyhZ9RanxftZ%2B8MM2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=5270fec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a>"},{"pid":"239cd4f4910e6c65ed7c9cfbb2fe950e4b632f2f","tid":1543570,"uid":